
Imogen is a family of inverse method theorem provers for intuitionistic logics.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Installation instructions
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

0) Install the MLton Standard ML compiler : http://mlton.org

1) Unpack Imogen to directory D

2) D/bin/build

3) (Optional) D/bin/build test

4) (Optional) D/bin/build doc

5) add D/bin to your path

6) Check the executable is sane
   imogen prop prove -i 'p => p'

